    <item>
      <title>Bay Street 称特朗普胜选将长期提振 TSX</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/bay-street-says-trump-win-to-boost-tsx-over-long-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bay Street 分析师和投资组合经理认为，尽管最初的市场反应导致加拿大股市落后于美国股市，但唐纳德·特朗普的胜利将从长期来看提振加拿大股市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/bay-street-says-trump-win-to-boost-tsx-over-long-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:01:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街押注特朗普取得回报，ETF 押注被证明是正确的</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/wall-street-s-trump-gamble-paying-off-as-etf-bets-vindicated</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员们不顾一切，投入数十亿美元购买大量 ETF，希望一旦唐纳德·特朗普再次当选总统，这些 ETF 将大获成功。现在，他们的赌注终于获得了回报。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/wall-street-s-trump-gamble-paying-off-as-etf-bets-vindicated</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 17:00:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>一些全球领导人对特朗普获胜感到惊讶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/some-global-leaders-surprised-at-trump-win-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界各国领导人对唐纳德·特朗普夺回白宫的现实做出了反应。中东和乌克兰战火纷飞，特朗普又承诺提高关税，盟友们正处在紧张时期。罗莎琳德·马西森报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-06/some-global-leaders-surprised-at-trump-win-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普政策为英国央行未来降息之路蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-policies-cloud-bank-of-england-s-path-to-future-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行本周几乎肯定会将利率再次下调四分之一个百分点，但唐纳德·特朗普的第二个美国总统任期给英国未来的政策放松带来了新的不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/trump-policies-cloud-bank-of-england-s-path-to-future-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 16:07:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选颠覆市场，特斯拉股价飙升，而电动汽车竞争对手股价下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/tesla-soars-as-musk-s-all-in-bet-on-trump-seen-reaping-rewards</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者押注唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫将使伊隆·马斯克的公司受益，特斯拉公司股价飙升——尽管其他电动汽车市场的前景愈发黯淡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/tesla-soars-as-musk-s-all-in-bet-on-trump-seen-reaping-rewards</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 09:02:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普卷土重来，美元飙升，新兴市场陷入困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周三，“特朗普交易”再度兴起，导致美元和美国国债收益率在特朗普当选后飙升，给新兴市场带来沉重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/emerging-currencies-slump-as-markets-lean-toward-a-trump-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 03:11:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的决定性胜利推动美元上涨，黄金和铜价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着唐纳德·特朗普重新入主白宫，黄金和铜价暴跌，美元飙升给大宗商品带来压力，而交易员则权衡他的观点对贸易、地缘政治和美国经济的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-05/gold-holds-steady-before-results-of-coin-toss-us-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Nov 2024 23:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
